                this document.
            </para>
        </introduction>
        
        <section>
            <title>Handling Paragraph</title>
            <content>
                <para>
                    As you might have observed already, most conceptual tag supports
                    the <legacyBold>&lt;para&gt;...&lt;/para&gt;</legacyBold> tag, 
                    which is used to create a paragraph in a help file.
                </para>
                <alert class="tip">
                    <para>
                        You can create a new line or line break using
                        <legacyBold>&lt;para/&gt;</legacyBold>.
                    </para>
                </alert>
            </content>
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <title>Handling Text Styling</title>
            <content>
                <para>
                    As expected, there is support for basic text styling:
                </para>
                <list class="bullet">
                <listItem>
                    <para>
                        Produce simple text styling of <legacyBold>Bold</legacyBold>,
                        using the <legacyBold>&lt;legacyBold&gt;</legacyBold> tag.
                    </para>
                </listItem>
                <listItem>
                    <para>
                        Produce simple text styling of <legacyItalic>Italic</legacyItalic>,
                        using the <legacyBold>&lt;legacyItalic&gt;</legacyBold> tag.
                    </para>
                </listItem>
                <listItem>
                    <para>
                        Produce simple text styling of <legacyUnderline>Underline</legacyUnderline>,
                        using the <legacyBold>&lt;legacyUnderline&gt;</legacyBold> tag.
                    </para>
                </listItem>
                <listItem>
                    <para>
                        Produce simple text styling of Base<superscript>Superscript</superscript>,
                        using the <legacyBold>&lt;superscript&gt;</legacyBold> tag.
                    </para>
                </listItem>
                <listItem>
                    <para>
                        Produce simple text styling of Base<subscript>Subscript</subscript>,
                        using the <legacyBold>&lt;subscript&gt;</legacyBold> tag.
                    </para>
                </listItem>
                </list>
            </content>
        </section>

